before you know it, OK?

184
00:12:17,431 --> 00:12:18,098
All right.

185
00:12:18,131 --> 00:12:19,765
Let's get going, Idate.

186
00:12:19,798 --> 00:12:20,265
-Right!

187
00:12:27,998 --> 00:12:28,798
-Come on.

188
00:12:28,831 --> 00:12:29,798
