odd one, aren't you?

250
00:16:00,165 --> 00:16:01,631
-You did very well, Idate.

251
00:16:01,665 --> 00:16:03,065
-You really came through.

252
00:16:03,098 --> 00:16:04,598
-Well, go on, then.

253
00:16:04,631 --> 00:16:05,398
This is your day.

254
00:16:05,431 --> 00:16:07,865
